description: Numerators of expansion of a function eta(x) related to Cremer points.
references: J. Milnor, Dynamics in One Complex Variable, Vieweg, 1999, p. 127.
formula: eta(x) is the limit of the sequence defined by eta_0 = -x/2; eta_{i+1} = eta_i + x^{i-1} eta_i^2.
author: _N. J. A. Sloane_, Jan 14 2001
